re playing a game.","Video frame rate contributes directly to a recording&#39;s overall quality and file size. It can be hard to find a good balance between quality and efficiency, but Bandicam allows you to set custom frame rates. This means you can find the sweet spot that&#39;s right for what you want your videos to do, and you don&#39;t have to worry about whether there is a predefined option that fits what you need. You can also enter custom resolutions, giving you even more control over the quality and efficiency of your recordings."]},"id":"9183c2e6-31b5-4b09-a135-e6f3641ffba8","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"46d24762-8331-46db-931c-3e189b723b4c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Bandicam is great video game recording software, but it has some noticeable lag while starting and stopping recordings. You can expect it to deliver high-quality recordings, though, and it has the settings you need to fine-tune those recordings. Powerful and easy-to-use tools complement the software&#39;s simple user interface. Bandicam strikes a good balance between depth and breadth, giving you a good selection of recording tools and keeping them effective."]},"id":"03ed2de5-8381-4124-a63d-4a1e7b80bc77","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58809","url":"/bandicam-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"dan-tennant","url":"/author/dan-tennant","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Dan Tennant","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"eocoVhBgsHkCaPAuPbt37k","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-02-11T20:54:14Z","datePublished":"2014-02-11T20:54:14Z","name":"Bandicam 2.1.3","synopsis":"Video game recording software is complex, and the software's performance depends on many variables. Bandicam has most of the tools and settings we look for in the best game recording software and it doesn't put a large strain on your computer.","review":{"rating":90,"verdict":"Ba